isValid

protected boolean isValid(Object object)
Validity of entered object is checked with Validator. In the case where relevant object is implementation of IClassValidator, validity is checked by calling for isValid method within object. Otherwise, validity is checked by calling for isValid method of DefaultObjectValidator.

Parameters:
object - Object to save search result
Returns:
whether valid
